data.description: WELCOME HOME!! Beautiful log cabin, located 15 minutes from Rogersville and 30 minutes from Kingsport, sits on 3.61 acres out in the country. Enjoy the peacefulness of nature while sitting by the pond! Huge master bedroom with a master bath, sunroom and spacious kitchen. Beautiful stone fireplace in the living room and dining room. Every bedroom has a fireplace and lots of closet space. 3 bonus rooms downstairs! This home offers plenty of space for family gatherings! Two car garage drive under and plenty of parking for an RV or boat. By the picnic area, there's a spot for your RV with septic and electric hookup! Solar panels are installed with a back up battery!This home has so many potentials and space to use for your liking. Call for a showing today!!
